<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transaction Notification - Cooperative Banking</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1976d2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .transaction-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1976d2;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1976d2;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Cooperative Banking</h1>
        <h2>Transaction Notification</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        
        <p>A {{transactionType}} transaction has been processed on your account.</p>
        
        <div class="transaction-details">
            <h3>Transaction Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Account Number:</strong> {{accountNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Transaction Type:</strong> {{transactionType}}</p>
            <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <span class="amount">₹{{amount}}</span></p>
            <p><strong>Current Balance:</strong> ₹{{balance}}</p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
            <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>Security Alert:</strong>
            <p>If you didn't perform this transaction, please contact us immediately at our customer support number or visit your nearest branch.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can view your complete transaction history by logging into your online banking account.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for banking with us!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Cooperative Banking Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>© 2024 Cooperative Banking. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
